main event: A civilian reported sighting a round bright white light moving northward in San Angelo, Texas on August 5, 1968.
interesting points: The observed object was described as being the size of a dollar,The observation type was classified as closed-visual,The sighting was part of Project Blue Book, which investigated UFOs,The observer did not complete the requested AF Form 117 within the 30-day period,The conclusion of the report indicated insufficient data for a scientific investigation.
witness description: a civilian resident of San Angelo, Texas
